  <summary date="2023-08-21T16:18:07Z" status="Introduced in House">Water Efficiency, Conservation, and Sustainability Act of 2022

This bill establishes multiple grants that support activities to incentivize efficient water use by customers of public water systems, reduce water losses and leaks in water systems, and promote the adoption of water-efficient plumbing codes.</summary>
